90
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:16,600
Umakyat tayo at tingnan natin.

91
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:17,600
Okay.

92
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:22,440
pasensya na po. pasensya na po.

93
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:24,040
Okay.

94
