155
00:11:06,560 --> 00:11:08,120
Hindi ko kayang iwan ka.

156
00:11:09,560 --> 00:11:10,880
Hindi ko kaya.

157
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:13,200
hindi ako aalis.

158
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:15,200
Hayaan mo na.

159
00:11:20,280 --> 00:11:21,640
Tumayo ka.

160
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:24,560
Mananatili ako sa iyo magdamag.

161
00:11:26,160 --> 00:11:27,160
Okay.

162
00:11:28,560 --> 00:11:29,800
Lagi kitang makakasama.

163
00:11:30,720 --> 00:11:31,720
Lagi akong mananatili sa iyo.

164
00:11:31,721 --> 00:11:33,880
Tapos kakantahin kita.

165
00:11:35,560 --> 00:11:36,679
Oo naman.

166
00:11:36,680 --> 00:11:37,680
Sige na.

167
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:33,080
Lol na lalaki.

168
00:12:52,400 --> 00:12:54,360
Bakit uminom ng marami
kung hindi mo kayang hawakan ang iyong alak?

169
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:56,280
Lol na lalaki.

170
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:06,480
Matulog ka na.

171
00:13:31,240 --> 00:13:34,080
Kayong dalawa, siguraduhing ilagay
nang maayos ang mga kandila.

172
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:35,400
- Oo, Mr. Wu.
- Xiao Li.

173
00:13:35,640 --> 00:13:37,199
Natapos mo na ba ang proposal
na hiniling ko sa iyo noong nakaraan?

174
00:13:37,200 --> 00:13:38,239
