- Matanda ka na. Itigil ang panonood nito.

183
00:13:59,440 --> 00:14:00,520
Ang kulay ng spray paint...

184
00:14:00,600 --> 00:14:02,000
dapat mayaman.

185
00:14:02,120 --> 00:14:03,919
- Okay, Mr. Wu.
- Ipagpatuloy mo.

186
00:14:03,920 --> 00:14:05,959
Busy ka. Busy kayong lahat.

187
00:14:05,960 --> 00:14:06,960
Xiao Shuai.

188
00:14:07,280 --> 00:14:08,320
Nandito ka pa?

189
00:14:08,440 --> 00:14:09,719
Bukod sa trabaho,

190
00:14:09,720 --> 00:14:11,800
